fields.label: Market Rental Rate
fields.name: lease_market_rental_rate
fields.instructions: This field will be displayed in the front (Property Details) along with the selected Rental Unit.

fields.label: Convert Rental Rate to Sort
fields.name: actual_rental_rate
fields.instructions: Enter the rental rate again, converting to $psf/year. Required field to allow the user to sort by price. Enter a decimal point.

fields.label: Total Building Size
fields.name: lease_total_building_size
fields.instructions: Enter number only.  Comma is formatted.

fields.label: Gross Leasable Area
fields.name: lease_gross_leasable_area
fields.instructions: Enter numbers only. Comma is formatted.

fields.label: Convert Lot Size to SF
fields.name: lease_convert_lot_size_to_sf
fields.instructions: Enter numbers only. Comma is formatted.

fields.label: Operating Expenses
fields.name: lease_operating_expenses
fields.instructions: Field is formatted with $ & PSF only.  Enter decimal point.

fields.label: Spaces
fields.name: lease_spaces
fields.instructions: After adding specific available spaces from "Spaces" Posts, Link one/more Spaces to include in here.

fields.label: Sale Price
fields.name: sale_price
fields.instructions: Enter numbers only. Comma is formatted.

fields.label: Building Size
fields.name: sale_building_size
fields.instructions: Enter number only.  Comma is formatted.

fields.label: Operating Expenses
fields.name: sale_operating_expenses
fields.instructions: Field is formatted with $ & PSF only.  Enter decimal point.

fields.label: Dock-High Loading Doors
fields.name: sale_dock_high_loading_doors
fields.instructions: Enter numbers only. Values are formatted as (2) 10' x 12'

fields.label: Drive In Grade-Level Doors
fields.name: sale_drive_in_grade_level_doors
fields.instructions: Enter numbers only. Values are formatted as (2) 10' x 12'

fields.label: Column Spacing
fields.name: sale_column_spacing
fields.instructions: Enter numbers only. Values are formatted as 10' x 12'
